				"description":{
					"value":"<p><b>Free Action</b></p><p>Special </p><p></p><p class=\"power-basics\"><b>Target: </b> The triggering creature</p><p class=\"power-basics\"><b>Attack: </b>+25 vs. AC</p><p><b>Hit: </b> 3d8 damage.</p><p><b>Special: </b> A creature slain by the heart rises as a free-willed Moilian zombie at the start of its next turn, appearing in the space where it died or in the nearest unoccupied space if that space is occupied. The Moilian zombie must be destroyed before the creature can be raised.</p>",
